      "original_name": "image25.png",
      "extracted_name": "image-025.png",
      "relative_path": "./images/image-025.png",
      "paragraph_index": 192,
      "paragraph_text": "",
      "previous_text": "泸源崖是泸沽湖的源头，也是泸沽湖湖水较深的地方，较深处可达90余米。此处石崖如削,景观独特。",
      "next_text": "b女神湾（重要景区）"
    },
    {
      "image_sequence": 26,
      "relationship_id": "rId32",
      "source_media_path": "word/media/image26.png",
      "original_name": "image26.png",
      "extracted_name": "image-026.png",
      "relative_path": "./images/image-026.png",
      "paragraph_index": 195,
      "paragraph_text": "",
      "previous_text": "女神湾是泸沽湖中一个安静的港湾，也是泸沽湖最美的湖湾之一，被游人称为东方夏威夷。",
      "next_text": "c五支洛码头（猪槽船）"
    },
