      "source_media_path": "word/media/image27.png",
      "original_name": "image27.png",
      "extracted_name": "image-027.png",
      "relative_path": "./images/image-027.png",
      "paragraph_index": 199,
      "paragraph_text": "",
      "previous_text": "猪槽船可以单买票也可以包船，记得讲价（对半砍）。",
      "next_text": "这个季节草是黄的、花没有开，所以选择选路1或4较为合适，只能看海鸥。"
    },
    {
      "image_sequence": 28,
      "relationship_id": "rId34",
      "source_media_path": "word/media/image28.png",
      "original_name": "image28.png",
      "extracted_name": "image-028.png",
