      "original_name": "image30.png",
      "extracted_name": "image-030.png",
      "relative_path": "./images/image-030.png",
      "paragraph_index": 210,
      "paragraph_text": "",
      "previous_text": "传说，在这里和心爱的人手牵手走过，就可以拥有长久的爱情。",
      "next_text": "f蒗放"
    },
    {
      "image_sequence": 31,
